subject: Track and Field
Pole Vault
lead_paragraph: Jenn Stuczynski, the Olympic silver medalist in the women’s pole vault, cleared 15 feet 9 ¾ inches to break a six-year-old American mark and win the Boston Indoor Games for the third straight year.
